<%= short_patient_name %> may get their <%= vaccination %> at school on <%= next_session_date %>.

<% if vaccine_is?("injection") %>Please make sure they have breakfast and encourage them to wear a short-sleeved shirt.<% end %>

<% if vaccine_is?("nasal") %>If your child has asthma, please let us know if they've had a flare-up of asthma symptoms in the 3 days before the vaccination is due to take place, or on the day of the vaccination. This includes wheezing or needing to use a reliever inhaler more than usual.<% end %>

If <%= short_patient_name %> is absent or unwell on the day of the vaccination session, contact us to ask about alternative sessions.

<%= subteam_name %>, <%= subteam_phone %>
